{"tid":512734,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[m記全翼]唔俾轉全翼又係契丹人管理之下既傑作","createTime":"2017-12-28T20:02:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-03T10:51:50.000Z","uid":60665,"like":64,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"ca676edd54d31a991995369f43ba40e1e6c67309","tid":512734,"uid":60665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T20:02:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/28/235201_db9b5840ce25a269b6b3ae8b65912647.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F28%2F235201_db9b5840ce25a269b6b3ae8b65912647.jpeg&h=31ff0a24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前停賣板雞，最後我估因為營業額真係明顯下降所以又死死氣出返黎<br />\n<br />\n點知仲未識死，又諗過第二樣縮數，唔俾人加野轉全翼<br />\n<br />\n最大問題係十幾年黎都俾，而家無啦啦突然就一刀切話依樣唔俾個樣唔俾，咁既做法先最令人反感<br />\n<br />\n契丹人既管理就係咁，只識做d令自已最大利益省到最多錢既方法，唔會諗班客受唔受同自已企業個image，諗著我點做你班客都要食我架啦，洗乜理你地<br />\n<br />\n咁管理法今日唔死遲早一日都死，日本麥當勞已經係例子"},{"pid":"0b263aa86eb716a606845d4b41d9b674848387fb","tid":512734,"uid":126053,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T20:08:55.000Z","msg":"食個包 菜都唔比人多<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"429d3edeea8e59933e30acc75aac93fe4bf65461","tid":512734,"uid":87613,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"0b263aa86eb716a606845d4b41d9b674848387fb","tid":512734,"uid":126053,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T20:08:55.000Z","msg":"食個包 菜都唔比人多<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T21:01:29.000Z","msg":"垃圾，生菜又唔係貴，俾得一片，subway都有得無限加菜啦"},{"pid":"32caa5f432fe5215670326cbdf73ec987624cf10","tid":512734,"uid":87613,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T21:02:09.000Z","msg":"新地唔加多d花生就唔好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a273d580bb827a74b324b4c27da602b0d31b7c3a","tid":512734,"uid":36049,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-2